    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that\u2019s reliable and still looks great hitting the road? I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive! It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-cared for, so it\u2019s ready for all your upcoming adventures. It\u2019s clean, comfortable, and runs like a charm. Come check it out\u2014I'd love for it to go to a good home!",
