    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a limited-slip differential with a 3.62 final drive ratio. Crucial preventative maintenance has been performed, including a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and a recent valve shim adjustment to ensure optimal valvetrain clearance. The chassis integrity is preserved with reinforced subframe mounting points and upgraded polyurethane bushings. It retains the factory-tuned suspension geometry, providing the communicative steering and balanced lateral grip these cars are known for. A mechanically honest example optimized for performance.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
