    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Looking for a reliable ride that\u2019s ready for your next adventure? This car has been such a joy to own\u2014it runs like a dream and has been super well-maintained. It\u2019s in great shape and perfect for someone who wants a solid, stylish vehicle without the brand-new price tag. I\u2019ve loved every mile in it, and I\u2019m sure you will too! Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come take it for a spin!",
